{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, Table 2 illustrates that the IAA value for TF exceeded that of disease mentions.",
    "In terms of key-sentence annotation, the IAA was measured at 0.752, and for the annotation between TF and disease relations within key-sentences, the IAA was higher at 0.892.",
    "In the review meeting phase, annotators from each group engaged in discussions to address and resolve discrepancies in the initial annotation results.",
    "Through these discussions, they collectively derived solutions.",
    "The acceptance of these solutions was determined independently by the annotators, and they were subsequently incorporated during the annotation revision phase."
  ]
}